videos.description: Samir Doughty starts the game hot from deep, connecting on his first two shots from beyond the arc to give Auburn an early lead.
videos.headline: Doughty drills back-to-back 3s for Auburn

videos.description: Jay Jay Chandler attacks the rack in transition, but has his shot denied at the rim by Anfernee McLemore, who blocks the shot off the backboard.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Auburn's McLemore swats shot off glass) 2020/03/04

videos.headline: Auburn's McLemore swats shot off glass

videos.description: J'Von McCormick throws up a lob to Jaylin Williams, who elevates to flush the alley-oop with authority.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Williams throws down vicious lefty jam for Auburn) 2020/03/04

videos.headline: Williams throws down vicious lefty jam for Auburn

videos.description: Jay Jay Chandler drives to the rim and Eurosteps through the Auburn defense for the basket plus the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Texas A&M's Chandler hits tough Eurostep in traffic) 2020/03/04

videos.headline: Texas A&M's Chandler hits tough Eurostep in traffic

videos.description: Emanuel Miller throws inside to Josh Nebo, who makes a great catch in the paint then rises up for the powerful flush.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Nebo rocks the rim for Texas A&M) 2020/03/04

videos.headline: Nebo rocks the rim for Texas A&M

videos.description: Texas A&M's Jay Jay Chandler picks J'Von McCormick's pocket and takes it the other way for the two-handed slam in transition.

videos.headline: Chandler strips defender and slams it home

videos.description: The Bachelor contestant and Auburn alum Madison Prewett helps pump up the Tigers crowd during a timeout.
